---
title: "System architecture — JEME/JEOE Earth Science Dashboard"
---
flowchart LR
    subgraph Sources [Data Sources]
        SS[Semantic Scholar<br/>Academic Graph]
        CR[Crossref<br/>REST API]
        UP[Unpaywall API]
        OA[OpenAlex API]
        Wiley[Wiley TDM]
        Else[Elsevier TDM]
        Cop[Copernicus]
    end
    subgraph Pipeline [Citation Analytics Pipeline]
        direction TB
        Seed[Seed paper<br/>identification] --> Collect[Citation<br/>collection]
        Collect --> Verify[Multi-agent<br/>verification<br/>5 agents]
        Verify --> PR[Peer-review<br/>filtering]
        PR --> Enrich[DAS / Methods<br/>enrichment<br/>Fig. 9]
        Enrich --> LLM[Gemini classifier<br/>engagement level<br/>research domain]
        LLM --> UQ[Three-phase<br/>uncertainty<br/>quantification]
    end
    subgraph Storage [Storage]
        JSON[(model_analyzed.json<br/>per model/mission)]
    end
    subgraph Frontend [React Dashboard]
        direction TB
        JEME[JEME<br/>8 models]
        JEOE[JEOE<br/>3 missions]
        JESP[JESP<br/>199 scientists]
        Network[Cross-model<br/>network analysis]
        Sphere[Earth-system<br/>sphere classification]
        MCL[MCL<br/>capability<br/>maturity]
    end

    Sources --> Pipeline
    Pipeline --> Storage
    Storage --> Frontend
    Storage --> Network
    Storage --> Sphere
    Storage --> MCL

    style Sources fill:#e3f2fd
